Fairphone Privacy Impact increases awareness about how your data is used. To learn more about how Privacy Impact is calculated, please visit
This app does not require any permissions and cannot access any of your personal data. It should be safe to use and doesn’t put your privacy at risk.

This app requires access to some personal data in order to work. Review the permissions below to ensure they make sense for the app’s functionality. If you have concerns, we recommend you read additional reviews or look for an alternative app.

This app requires access to a considerable amount of personal data in order to work. Review the permissions below to ensure they make sense for the app’s functionality. If you do not trust the app developer, we recommend looking for an alternative app.

This app needs access to a great deal of personal data in order to work. Review the permissions below to ensure they make sense for the app’s functionality. If you do not trust the app developer, we highly recommend looking for an alternative app.
Fairphone wants you to know how your data is used by the apps you download. The Privacy Impact level is based on app permissions that have direct access to your personal data.

Turn on if you would like to receive notifications from this app. Notifications appear at the top of the screen. If you select Priority, notifications will also be shown when your device is set to priority interruptions only.
Never show notifications from this app.
Notifications appear first on the list. You\'ll still receive them when your device is set to priority interruptions only.
Stop showing Privacy Impact and Notification Settings for my apps. You can always turn it back on in the settings.
